General.Name: Deep Field Technologies Inc
General.Description: Deep Field Technologies, Inc. engages in painting and repairing automobiles, and the sale of automotive parts, accessories, and supplies in the People's Republic of China. It also operates as an auto insurance agent. As of December 31, 2006, Deep Field operated 12 automotive repair centers in Beijing. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
